import React, { useState } from 'react';

const MAIN_GIF     = "data:image/gif;base64,";
const CRY_GIF      = "data:image/gif;base64,";
const KILL_GIF     = "data:image/gif;base64,";
const NO_CHOICE_GIF = "data:image/gif;base64,";
const YES_GIF      = "data:image/gif;base64,";

export default function App() {
  const [noCount, setNoCount] = useState(0);
  const [yesPressed, setYesPressed] = useState(false);
  const [noPosition, setNoPosition] = useState({ x: 0, y: 0 });

  const phrases = [
    "No",
    "Are you sure?",
    "Pookie please ",
    "Don't do this to me ",
    "You're breaking my heart ",
    "I'm gonna cry... ",
    "Think about it!",
    "Are you absolutely certain?",
    "This could be a mistake!",
    "Really??",
    "Pwease ",
    "I'll be sad...",
    "You can't say no!",
    "Give me a chance!",
    "Don't be like that ",
    "Please please please!",
    "I'm begging you!",
    "Just say yes!",
    "Come on!",
    "Why not? ",
    "PLEASE SAY YES!",
    "I'll find you... ",
    "I'll KILL YOU ",
    "Say yes already! "
  ];

  const getNoButtonText = () => phrases[Math.min(noCount, phrases.length - 1)];

  const handleNoHover = () => {
    setNoCount(c => c + 1);
    const newX = Math.random() * (window.innerWidth - 300) - (window.innerWidth / 2 - 150);
    const newY = Math.random() * (window.innerHeight - 200) - (window.innerHeight / 2 - 100);
    setNoPosition({ x: newX, y: newY });
  };

  // Sticker + message selon nombre de "No"
  const getSticker = () => {
    if (noCount >= 21) return { gif: NO_CHOICE_GIF, msg: "You have no choice now!! ", color: '#ff3d7f' };
    if (noCount >= 11) return { gif: KILL_GIF,      msg: "I'll KILL YOU if you say no again!! ", color: '#cc0000' };
    if (noCount >= 5)  return { gif: CRY_GIF,       msg: "I'm gonna cry... ", color: '#ff3d7f' };
    return { gif: MAIN_GIF, msg: null, color: '#ff3d7f' };
  };

  const { gif, msg, color } = getSticker();

  //  PAGE YES 
  if (yesPressed) {
    return (
      <div style={{
        minHeight: '100vh',
        background: '#ffc9d9',
        display: 'flex',
        flexDirection: 'column',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        fontFamily: '"Quicksand", sans-serif',
        position: 'relative',
        overflow: 'hidden'
      }}>
        <style>{`
          @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
          @keyframes fall { to { transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(720deg); } }
          @keyframes popIn { 0%{transform:scale(0);opacity:0} 80%{transform:scale(1.1)} 100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1} }
        `}</style>

        {[...Array(60)].map((_, i) => (
          <div key={i} style={{
            position: 'absolute',
            width: '12px', height: '12px',
            background: ['#ff6b9d','#ffd93d','#6bcf7f','#4d9fff','#ff8364','#c780e8'][i % 6],
            left: `${Math.random() * 100}%`,
            top: '-10px',
            animation: `fall ${2 + Math.random() * 2}s linear infinite`,
            animationDelay: `${Math.random() * 3}s`,
            borderRadius: Math.random() > 0.5 ? '50%' : '2px',
          }} />
        ))}

        <img src={YES_GIF} alt="yes!" style={{
          width: '280px',
          height: '280px',
          objectFit: 'contain',
          animation: 'popIn 0.6s ease-out forwards',
          marginBottom: '10px'
        }} />

        <h1 style={{ fontSize: '80px', fontWeight: '700', color: '#ff6b9d', margin: '10px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}>
           Yipee! 
        </h1>
        <h2 style={{ fontSize: '50px', fontWeight: '700', color: '#ff3d7f', margin: '10px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}>
          Good Boy! 
        </h2>
        <p style={{ fontSize: '28px', color: '#ff3d7f', fontWeight: '600' }}>I'm so happy! </p>
      </div>
    );
  }

  //  PAGE PRINCIPALE 
  return (
    <div style={{
      minHeight: '100vh',
      background: '#ffc9d9',
      display: 'flex',
      flexDirection: 'column',
      alignItems: 'center',
      justifyContent: 'center',
      fontFamily: '"Quicksand", sans-serif',
      padding: '20px'
    }}>
      <style>{`
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
        @keyframes float { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(-15px)} }
        @keyframes shake { 0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)} 25%{transform:translateX(-6px)} 75%{transform:translateX(6px)} }
        @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{transform:scale(1)} 50%{transform:scale(1.05)} }
        .yes-btn { transition: all 0.2s; }
        .yes-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.07); }
        .yes-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
      `}</style>

      <h1 style={{
        fontSize: '56px', fontWeight: '700', color: '#ff6b9d',
        marginBottom: '10px', textAlign: 'center', lineHeight: '1.2'
      }}>
         Will you be my Valentine? 
      </h1>

      {/* Sticker central unique */}
      <img
        src={gif}
        alt="sticker"
        style={{
          width: '260px',
          height: '260px',
          objectFit: 'contain',
          margin: '20px 0',
          animation: noCount >= 11
            ? 'shake 0.4s ease-in-out infinite'
            : 'float 3s ease-in-out infinite'
        }}
      />

      {/* Message sous le sticker */}
      {msg && (
        <p style={{
          fontSize: noCount >= 21 ? '32px' : '26px',
          fontWeight: '700',
          color: color,
          textAlign: 'center',
          marginBottom: '10px',
          animation: 'pulse 1s ease-in-out infinite'
        }}>
          {msg}
        </p>
      )}

      {/* Boutons */}
      <div style={{
        display: 'flex', gap: '20px', marginTop: '20px',
        flexWrap: 'wrap', justifyContent: 'center',
        position: 'relative', minHeight: '100px'
      }}>
        <button
          className="yes-btn"
          onClick={() => setYesPressed(true)}
          style={{
            backgroundColor: 'white', color: '#ff3d7f',
            border: '3px solid #ff3d7f', borderRadius: '30px',
            padding: `${15 + noCount * 4}px ${50 + noCount * 8}px`,
            fontSize: `${26 + noCount * 5}px`,
            fontWeight: '700', cursor: 'pointer',
            fontFamily: 'inherit', boxShadow: '0 4px 0 #ff3d7f',
            transition: 'all 0.3s ease'
          }}
        >
          Yes
        </button>

        {noCount < phrases.length && noCount < 21 && (
          <button
            onMouseEnter={handleNoHover}
            style={{
              backgroundColor: 'white', color: '#999',
              border: '3px solid #ddd', borderRadius: '30px',
              padding: '15px 50px',
              fontSize: Math.max(26 - noCount * 2, 10) + 'px',
              fontWeight: '700', cursor: 'pointer',
              fontFamily: 'inherit', boxShadow: '0 4px 0 #ddd',
              position: noCount > 0 ? 'fixed' : 'relative',
              left: noCount > 0 ? `calc(50% + ${noPosition.x}px)` : 'auto',
              top: noCount > 0 ? `calc(50% + ${noPosition.y}px)` : 'auto',
              transform: noCount > 0 ? 'translate(-50%, -50%)' : 'none',
              zIndex: 1000
            }}
          >
            {getNoButtonText()}
          </button>
        )}
      </div>

      {noCount > 0 && noCount < 5 && (
        <p style={{ marginTop: '20px', fontSize: '22px', fontWeight: '600', color: '#ff3d7f', textAlign: 'center' }}>
          I know you want to say yes! 
        </p>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
